      "researchJobs": "Scheduled automated analysis jobs that scan instrument universes and publish opportunities to the recommendations feed. Each job has a schedule, universe configuration, and run history.",
      "sectors": "Sector groupings mapping instruments to industry sectors for the sentiment-by-sector chart. Includes system-default sectors and user-customizable groupings."
